      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
                  <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan>
                  <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan>.
               <lb n="2"/>
                 <persName>
                    <name type="gentilicium" key="Julius">Iulio</name>
                    <name type="cognomen" key="Erotis">E
               <lb n="3" break="no"/>        
                     rot<hi rend="apex">i</hi></name>
                 </persName>, 
                 <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> 
               <lb n="4"/>
                  annis <num value="6">VI</num>,
               <lb n="5"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="praenomen" key="Titus"><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan></name>
                     <name type="gentilicium" key="Flavius"><expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>lavius</ex></expan></name>
                     <name type="cognomen" key="Gemellus">G<choice><corr>e</corr><sic>i</sic></choice>me
               <lb n="6" break="no"/>
                     llus</name>
                  </persName>,
                  <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan>
               <lb n="7"/>
                  <expan><abbr>cl</abbr><ex>assis</ex></expan>
                  <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetoriae</ex></expan>
                  <expan><abbr>Mis</abbr><ex>enensis</ex></expan>,
               <lb n="8"/>
                  <expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan>
                  <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan>
                  fecit.               
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the divine spirits. Titus Flavius Gemellus, a soldier of the praetorian Fleet of
               Misenum, made [this] for well-deserving Julius Erotis, [who] lived for six years.</p>
         </div>
